dc_title_s: Shipping Fairways in the Gulf of Mexico, 2012
dc_description_s: This polyline dataset shows the major shipping fairways in the Gulf of Mexico region. This layer includes data for Q3 2012. This layer is intended to assist users in locating and analyzing information related to shipping fairways in the Gulf of Mexico and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. Hart Energy Publishing. (2012). Shipping Fairways in the Gulf of Mexico, 2012. Hart Energy Publishing. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/jd693bq3824. This release is intended to replace all previous datasets. This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
